  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Warpips</strong> is what would happen if Command and Conquer and Nexus Wars had a baby made out of tanks and napalm! Set loose the engine of war and watch the chaos of physics-based combat explode onto the battlefield! Assemble your army from a diverse roster of infantry, vehicles and airplanes. Deploy troops, call down airstrikes, and launch missiles - all without that pesky micromanagement.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291010/extras/9229854eeb6031cabaf30f1bda2d57aa.webp?t=1770912777\" width=340 height=40 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Focus on the big picture; no complex micro<br></li><li>Each round lasts between 10-20 minutes<br></li><li>Easy to learn, hard to master</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291010/extras/b9bfd9e77a0f946da4ca1eb1d5c867d7.poster.avif?t=1770912777\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291010/extras/b9bfd9e77a0f946da4ca1eb1d5c867d7.webm?t=1770912777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291010/extras/b9bfd9e77a0f946da4ca1eb1d5c867d7.mp4?t=1770912777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291010/extras/1aa2e3134366d3650b5c7f6f882cfa26.webp?t=1770912777\" width=340 height=40 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Buy the game - you get the game<br></li><li>No microtransactions<br></li><li>No pay to win</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset